#. module: catering
#: model:mail.template,body_html:catering.mail_template_54
msgid ""
"<p style=\"border-radius: 0px; border-style: none; padding: 0px; margin: 0px 0 16px 0; border-left-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; border-top-width: 0px;\">\n"
"          Hello!\n"
"        </p>\n"
"        <p style=\"border-radius: 0px; border-style: none; padding: 0px; margin: 0px 0 16px 0; border-left-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; border-top-width: 0px;\">\n"
"          We know that the food is a huge part of what makes any event memorable, and we’re excited to share our latest\n"
"          <strong style=\"border-radius: 0px; border-style: none; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; font-weight: bolder;\">\n"
"          Event Food Catalog\n"
"          </strong>\n"
"          with you. It’s packed with options ranging from elegant plated dinners and interactive food stations to creative\n"
"          cocktail hour bites.\n"
"        </p>\n"
"        <p style=\"border-radius: 0px; border-style: none; padding: 0px; margin: 0px 0 16px 0; border-left-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; border-top-width: 0px;\">\n"
"          You can view the full catalog in attachment\n"
"        </p>\n"
"        <p style=\"border-radius: 0px; border-style: none; padding: 0px; margin: 0px 0 16px 0; border-left-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; border-top-width: 0px;\">\n"
"          Please consider this catalog as a <em>starting point</em>. Our biggest commitment is flexibility—everything you see\n"
"          (and even things you don't!) can be fully\n"
"          <strong style=\"border-radius: 0px; border-style: none; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; font-weight: bolder;\">\n"
"          customized and adjusted</strong>\n"
"          to fit your specific needs, theme, budget, and any dietary restrictions. Whether you’re planning a large corporate\n"
"          gala or an intimate family celebration, we're here to design a menu that's uniquely yours.\n"
"        </p>\n"
"        <p style=\"border-radius: 0px; border-style: none; padding: 0px; margin: 0px 0 16px 0; border-left-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; border-top-width: 0px;\">\n"
"          We look forward to helping you create an unforgettable culinary experience!\n"
"        </p>\n"
"        <p style=\"border-radius: 0px; border-style: none; padding: 0px; margin: 0px 0 16px 0; border-left-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; border-top-width: 0px;\">\n"
"          Warmly,\n"
"        </p>\n"
"    "
msgstr ""
"<p style=\"border-radius: 0px; border-style: none; padding: 0px; margin: 0px "
"0 16px 0; border-left-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-right-"
"width: 0px; border-top-width: 0px;\">\n"
"          Bonjour !\n"
"        </p>\n"
"        <p style=\"border-radius: 0px; border-style: none; padding: 0px; "
"margin: 0px 0 16px 0; border-left-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; "
"border-right-width: 0px; border-top-width: 0px;\">\n"
"          Nous savons que la restauration joue un rôle clé dans la réussite "
"de tout événement, et nous sommes ravis de vous faire découvrir notre tout "
"dernier\n"
"          <strong style=\"border-radius: 0px; border-style: none; padding: "
"0px; margin: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-"
"right-width: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; font-weight: bolder;\">\n"
"          catalogue de restauration événementielle.\n"
"          </strong>\n"
"          Il regroupe une large sélection de propositions, allant de dîners "
"élégants servis à l’assiette et stations culinaires interactives à des\n"
"          bouchées créatives pour vos cocktails.\n"
"        </p>\n"
"        <p style=\"border-radius: 0px; border-style: none; padding: 0px; "
"margin: 0px 0 16px 0; border-left-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; "
"border-right-width: 0px; border-top-width: 0px;\">\n"
"          Consultez l’intégralité du catalogue en pièce jointe\n"
"        </p>\n"
"        <p style=\"border-radius: 0px; border-style: none; padding: 0px; "
"margin: 0px 0 16px 0; border-left-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; "
"border-right-width: 0px; border-top-width: 0px;\">\n"
"          Merci de considérer ce catalogue comme un <em>point de départ</"
"em>. Notre engagement principal est la flexibilité : tout ce que vous y "
"trouverez\n"
"          (et même ce que vous n’y trouverez pas !) peut être entièrement\n"
"          <strong style=\"border-radius: 0px; border-style: none; padding: "
"0px; margin: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-"
"right-width: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; font-weight: bolder;\">\n"
"          personnalisé et ajusté</strong>\n"
"          en fonction de vos besoins spécifiques, de votre thème, de votre "
"budget et de vos éventuelles contraintes alimentaires. Que vous organisiez "
"un grand gala d’entreprise\n"
"          ou une réception familiale intimiste, nous sommes à vos côtés pour "
"concevoir un menu qui vous ressemble.\n"
"        </p>\n"
"        <p style=\"border-radius: 0px; border-style: none; padding: 0px; "
"margin: 0px 0 16px 0; border-left-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; "
"border-right-width: 0px; border-top-width: 0px;\">\n"
"          Nous avons hâte de vous accompagner dans la création d’une "
"expérience culinaire inoubliable !\n"
"        </p>\n"
"        <p style=\"border-radius: 0px; border-style: none; padding: 0px; "
"margin: 0px 0 16px 0; border-left-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; "
"border-right-width: 0px; border-top-width: 0px;\">\n"
"          Bien cordialement,\n"
"        </p>\n"
"    "

